OL,3,CAverage energy bill to fall by 12%
OL,4,Cfrom April, Ofgem announces
OL,6,Fsaid the fall in the price cap would
OL,7,Fsee energy charges reach the lowest
OL,8,Flevel since Russia's invasion of
OL,9,FUkraine in February 2022, which caused
OL,10,Fa spike in the wholesale market,
OL,11,Fdriving up costs for suppliers and
OL,12,Fcustomers.
OL,14,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,15,FBrearley called the drop "good news"
OL,16,Fbut warned "there are still big issues
OL,17,Fthat we must tackle head-on to ensure
OL,18,Fwe build a system that's more
OL,19,Fresilient for the long term and fairer
OL,20,Fto customers."
