OL,4,Cfrom April, Ofgem announces
OL,6,FHe said the regulator is looking to
OL,7,Faddress the risk of high levels of
OL,8,Fdebt in the system and said it will be
OL,9,Ftaking a step back to look at
OL,10,Faffordability across the market for
OL,11,Fstruggling customers.
OL,13,FMr Brearley added that in the long
OL,14,Fterm Ofgem "needs to think about what
OL,15,Fmore can be done for those who simply
OL,16,Fcannot afford to pay their energy
OL,17,Fbills even as prices fall.
